## Get started 

```
docker compose up -d
```

## Testing 


```
docker compose run --rm node npm i

# run unit tests
docker compose run --rm node npm run test

# run e2e tests
docker compose run --rm node npm run test:e2e
```

## API Usage

Endpoint: http://localhost:8080

POST /api/image-input
{
    min_level: number
    image: string
}

### Examples

```bash
curl -XPOST localhost:8080/api/image-input -H "Content-type: application/json" -d '{ "min_level": 100, "image": "data:image/png;base64," }'

```
